            An object table to track users and their demographics. The users will presumably participate in activities.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/trails"><strong>Trails</strong></a><br>
            An object table to track a unique trail that an activity was completed on.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/categories"><strong>Categories</strong></a><br>
            An object table to manage the different trail categories such as hiking, biking, etc.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/activities"><strong>Activities</strong></a><br>
            A transaction table to record an activity that a user participates in, such as hiking or biking on a trail.
        </p>
